dc_title_s: Michigan, Wisconsin, Iowa, and Minnesota; drawn and engraved by J. Bartholomew.
dc_description_s: Washington and Greenwich prime meridians. "Printed in colours by Schenck & MacFarlane, Edinburgh." Shows county outlines. Shows cities and towns.
